high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the wall. Turn left and face the fridge. Look up at the fridge.
Open the fridge and take out the purple fruit on the shelf and shut the door.
Turn left and walk turning right facing the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and put the fruit inside.  After a few seconds open the door and take the fruit back out.
Turn to the left facing the sink.
Put the fruit on the counter to the right.
anns.task_desc: To take the fruit out of the fridge to be moved to the microwave and counter.

high_descs: Turn to the right, head to the fridge
Open the fridge, take the plum out of the fridge
Close the fridge, head to the left
Open the door to the microwave, put the plum in the microwave, Close the door to the microwave,
run the microwave for 4 seconds, Open the door to the microwave, take the plum out
Close the door to the microwave, put the plum on the counter
anns.task_desc: Microwave a plum from the fridge for 4 seconds

high_descs: Open the fridge and take out a potato, then close it.
Walk in front of the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave to heat it, then remove it.
Turn to your left, facing the sink.
Place the potato on the edge of the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato to place on a table.
